body: Remember to delete p built before launch
Rename dotenv spec to something that is more meaningful. Travis and Heroku don't use dotenv
Did we want to merge into master with this? or does it have development changes in it already?
@namuunaa Let's make it say "You have 1 hour" (instead of hours)
@DillonBArevalo Remember to take out the p statements!
Controller tests are failing as predicted. Will merge as Ransom is updating the controller tests.
This passes all rspec tests locally, but Travis is failing due to a bug:
https://github.com/travis-ci/travis-ci/issues/7685
I don't see the tests running? It doesn't modify anything being tested so i'm going to merge it anyways though.
Travis is breaking in the cannot-run-rake way that it was yesterday (bug on their end). We are confident in our local tests, so merging now.
